{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"StyleSheet.parentStyleSheet","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/parentStyleSheet","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/disabled\"><code>disabled</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/href\"><code>href</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/media\"><code>media</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/ownerNode\"><code>ownerNode</code></a></li><li><em><code>parentStyleSheet</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/title\"><code>title</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/type\"><code>type</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n </div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"概要","isH3":false,"content":"<p>対象のスタイルシートを含む親スタイルシートが存在する場合は、それを返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>parentStyleSheetObj</var> = <var>stylesheet</var>.parentStyleSheet\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"注記","isH3":false,"content":"<p>対象スタイルシートがトップレベルのスタイルシートの場合、または対象スタイルシートがインクルードをサポートしていない場合、戻り値は <code>null</code> となります。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> stylesheet <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>styleSheets<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 文書中の最初のスタイルシート</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 親スタイルシートが存在する場合はそれを、</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 無ければ自身への参照を変数 sheet に代入しています。</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>parentStyleSheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  sheet <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>parentStyleSheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  sheet <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2000/REC-DOM-Level-2-Style-20001113/stylesheets.html#StyleSheets-StyleSheet-parentStyleSheet\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">parentStyleSheet</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://dev.w3.org/csswg/cssom/#widl-StyleSheet-parentStyleSheet\" title=\"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概要","id":"summary"},{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"注記","id":"notes"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specification"}],"summary":"対象のスタイルシートを含む親スタイルシートが存在する場合は、それを返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"StyleSheet.parentStyleSheet","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Stylesheet.parentStyleSheet","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"StyleSheet.parentStyleSheet","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"stylesheet.parentStyleSheet","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/stylesheet/parentsty